#### [NEW] [sync.ts](file:///c:/Users/raksh/Desktop/GrocerySho_List/backend/sync.ts)

Two new endpoints:

**`GET /api/sync/pull?since=<timestamp>`**
- Returns all records (across all tables) modified after `since` for the authenticated user
- Includes deleted records (so mobile can remove them locally)
- Response shape:
```json
{
  "categories": [...],
  "masterItems": [...],
  "shoppingLists": [...],
  "shoppingListItems": [...],
  "purchaseHistory": [...],
  "serverTime": "2024-01-15T12:00:00Z"
}
```

**`POST /api/sync/push`**
- Receives an array of local changes from the mobile
- Each change has: `uuid`, `table`, `data`, `updated_at`
- Server applies each change using "last write wins" (compares timestamps)
- Returns the final server version of each pushed record

