#### [NEW] [sync_engine.dart](file:///c:/Users/raksh/Desktop/GrocerySho_List/frontend_mobile/lib/data/sync_engine.dart)

The brain of offline-first. Handles:

1. **Pull**: Fetch changes from server → update local SQLite
2. **Push**: Send local dirty records → server → clear dirty flag
3. **Conflict resolution**: Last-write-wins based on `updated_at`
4. **Connectivity monitoring**: Auto-sync when internet returns

```dart
class SyncEngine {
  // Called when app starts or connectivity changes
  Future<void> sync() async {
    if (!await hasInternet()) return;
    
    await pushLocalChanges();  // Send our offline changes first
    await pullServerChanges(); // Then get what others changed
  }
}
```

